    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Honest Deal \u2013 A Budget-Friendly Project Car with Potential!** Looking for an affordable entry-level vehicle or a parts car? This one is priced to reflect its true condition \u2014 it shows significant wear, has visible body damage, and will need some mechanical attention. It's not a daily driver in its current state, but for the right buyer \u2014 a DIY enthusiast, a parts hunter, or someone with the skills to bring it back to life \u2014 this could be a great opportunity. We believe in full transparency, so what you see is what you get. Come take a look and decide for yourself!",
      "price": 6000.0,
